      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the detail. when i was doing my rotation with a similar patient with these same symptoms, the attending kept bringing up the possibility of drug-seeking behavior or non-compliance with meds.\n\nis that something i should be specifically looking for or asking about with mr. washington? or is that just a stereotype i should ignore?",
